                <mxCell id="step2" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;2. LLM意图识别 → 选择MCP工具&lt;br&gt;工具: query_energy_data&lt;br&gt;参数: {building_id: &quot;BLD-001&quot;, &lt;br&gt;       start_date: &quot;2026-03-03&quot;,&lt;br&gt;       end_date: &quot;2026-03-09&quot;,&lt;br&gt;       metrics: [&quot;electricity_kwh&quot;]}&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#C8E6C9;strokeColor=#2E7D32;fontSize=9;align=left;" parent="1" vertex="1">
